n<a href=\"http://www.fhs.gov.hk/tc_chi/main_ser/child_health/child_health_recommend.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fhs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fmain_ser%2Fchild_health%2Fchild_health_recommend.html&d=TX7dcU1hfrmzBqCl9MW4zL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a19c9121\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fhs.gov.hk/tc_chi/main_ser/child_health/child_health_recommend.html</a><br />\n大陸人需要果種係三合一，香港果種係四合一(白喉、破傷風、無細胞型百日咳及滅活小兒麻痺混合疫苗)，不過係類似的野黎，合共要打4次<br />\n<br />\n呢d針返過小學都會打曬架啦"},{"pid":"8da34f0bc711477a873ca3d775633d8e2b23004f","tid":751961,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"反吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}